{"type":null,"faqId":38959,"title":"手环如何连接另一部手机？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.33333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.33333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:14pt;}\n.p5{text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.11111111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n\"一个手环同一时间只能连接一部手机，手环和手机连接成功后其他手机无法搜索到手环。如果您要换一部手机连接手环，请先解除手环和第一部手机的绑定。<br>\n1.Android用户<br>\n（1）请打开APP，点击左上角手环图标进入到设置界面，点击界面最下方的“解除绑定”按钮。<br>\n（2）如果您的手环处于和APP连接状态不稳定的状态下，无法在APP上执行解除绑定/取消配对时，请打开手机蓝牙设置页面，选择取消配对。<br>\n2.iOS用户：请在手机蓝牙，我的设备”中选择zero手环，点击“忽略此设备” 然后使用另一部手机连接手环。\"\n<br>\n<br>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4269","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":62,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}